body:
Remember When you entered the **Minecraft Forums** and had seen some people saying about a **Monster** that lives on the caves? So, the **White Eyes**, is the antecessor of _Herobrine_. **The White Eyes** Will attack you on the **Darkness**, He **Breathe Behind** you, and when you least expect, You are **dead**.

If you are **without any armor**, He is **HitKill**;
Look **Around** When **Mining**;
He **always** Will spy you on the _Underground_.
